app_description: Logseq is a joyful open source outliner that works on top of local plain text Markdown and Org mode files. Use it to write organize and share your thoughts keep your to do list and build your own digital garden. Logseq includes the following features: 1. Backlink 2. Knowledge Graph 3. Page and block references 4. Page and block embeds 5. Tasks Todos 6. SRS Cards 7. Zotero integration 8. Youtube Twitter etc. integration 9. Audio recorder 10. Powerful queries 11. Whiteboards
